<div id="notification"></div>
<section class="section hero-banner firs-time-buyers hero-bg">
    <div class="container content-overlay">
        <div class="banner-block">

            <div class="banner-content">
                <div class="banner-text">
                    <h1 class="title">
                        <span>For </span>
                        <span>First time</span>
                        <span class="title_graident graident_4">Buyers</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="mt-3">
                        We understand that buying a PC can be intimidating, that's why we've made it easy with buttons and sliders -  Just pick your purpose and budget and voila! We'll take care of the rest, no jargon, no fuss. Plus, you get to avoid talking to real people, which is a bonus, right?
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="banner-visuals">
                <img src="~/assest/images/performance.webp">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section id="findPC" class="find-pc">
    <div class="container-fluid layout-fixed">
        <div class="find-pc-container">

            <div class="find-pc-content">
                <div class="section-head">
                    <h1>Find your PC</h1>
                    <div class="step-control-buttons">
                        <div class="nav nav-pills pill-custom" id="cpc-tab" role="tablist">
                            <button class="nav-link active" id="tab-choose" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#target-choose" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-choose" aria-selected="true">

                                <div class="btn-border">
                                    <div class="btn-border-top"></div>
                                    <div class="btn-text">Choose Preferences</div>
                                    <div class="btn-border-bottom"></div>
                                </div>
                            </button>
                            <button class="nav-link" id="tab-result" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#target-result" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-result" aria-selected="false">
                                <div class="btn-border" role="presentation">
                                    <div class="btn-border-top"></div>
                                    <div class="btn-text">View PCs</div>
                                    <div class="btn-border-bottom"></div>
                                </div>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>


                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="target-choose" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-choose">
                        <form name="formBudget" id="formBudget">
                            <p>Why settle for a one-size-fits-all PC when you can customize your own with just a few clicks of our magic buttons and slider</p>

                            <div class=" mb-2" id="error_alert" style="display: none;">
                                <small class="alert alert-warning d-inline p-2 rounded"><span class="flat-icon flaticon-info me-2"></span> Please complete all the steps</small>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row" style="margin:3%">
                            <div class="preference d-flex justify-content-around">
                                <div class="card" style="width: 33%;background-color: #dafffb;">
                                    <img src="~/assest/images/gaming.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="" style="width: 100%; height: 500px;">

                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <h5 class="card-title">Performence beast</h5>
                                        <p class="card-text">These are the computers that focused on performence.it's prefered for gaming, video editing, high coding works</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card" style="width: 33%;background-color: #dafffb;">
                                    <img src="~/assest/images/homecpu.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="..." style="width: 100%; height: 500px;">

                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <center>
                                            <h5 class="card-title">Home computers</h5>
                                            <p class="card-text">Home computers are mainly specified for minimal tasks like word processing, spreadsheets, email, accounting.</p>
                                        </center>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card" style="width: 33%;background-color: #dafffb;">
                                    <img src="~/assest/images/modrate.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="..." style="width: 100%; height: 500px;">

                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <h5 class="card-title">All rounder</h5>
                                        <p class="card-text">Modrate is a mixture of these two types which can push You to simple tasks and a descent level gaming.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                            <input type="hidden" name="input_usecase" id="input_usecase">
                            <input type="hidden" name="input_budget" id="input_budget">
                            <input type="hidden" name="input_accessories" id="input_accessories">
                        </form>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="target-result" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-result">
                        <div>
                            <h2>Please choose the preferences for result!</h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="fixed-element">
                <img src="~/assest/images/console.webp">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="cpc-key-features mb-0">

    <div class="container layout-fixed">
        <div class="section-head">
