                                    <p>What sets us apart is our experience and expertise. We've been building PCs for over 10 years and our team is made up of gamers and professionals with specific interests in graphics and video. This gives us a unique understanding of what it takes to create a top-performing PC that meets the demands of our customers.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-5">
                            <div class="cpc-feature">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <figure class="icon m-0"><img src="~/assest/images/icon-pc-performance.png"></figure>
