                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-5">
                            <div class="cpc-feature">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <figure class="icon m-0"><img src="~/assest/images/icon-pc-cpu.png"></figure>
                                    <div class="ms-3">
                                        <h5 class="text-uppercase">A Work of Art</h5>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="feature-content">
                                    <p>We use top-notch components and pay close attention to detail in every aspect of our builds. Our team of experts, with a passion for gaming and professional graphics, use their years of experience to craft PCs that exceed expectations and cater to individual needs. Trust us to deliver a dependable and visually impressive computer, tailored to your specifications.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-5">
                            <div class="cpc-feature">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <figure class="icon m-0"><img src="~/assest/images/icon-pc-maintenance.png"></figure>
                                    <div class="ms-3">
                                        <h5 class="text-uppercase">We’re Available! </h5>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="feature-content">
                                    <p>We prioritize customer service and make ourselves easily accessible through phone and email. With us, you can directly speak to a real person and receive personalized assistance with no pressure to make a purchase. Our goal is to ensure our customers make informed decisions and are completely satisfied with their purchase.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

